   347→ *
   348→ * For example if the value were "client, proxy1, proxy2"
   349→ * you would receive the array `["client", "proxy1", "proxy2"]`
   350→ * where "proxy2" is the furthest down-stream and "proxy1" and
   351→ * "proxy2" were trusted.
